    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to get this gorgeous ride into the hands of a new owner. Honestly, it\u2019s a total gem\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, so it\u2019s in truly pristine shape inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take a look, and see just how beautiful it is in person!",
      "price": 44900.0,
