    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera represents the pinnacle of the 996.2 generation, featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve. The powertrain is mated to a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle and a rare factory-spec limited-slip differential. This specimen is mechanically impeccable, featuring a proactive dual-row ceramic IMS bearing retrofit and a recent bore-scoping confirming zero cylinder wall scoring. The suspension maintains its factory-spec geometry with original Bilstein dampers, while the braking system utilizes four-piston monoblock calipers for exceptional thermal management and pedal feel. A true turn-key enthusiast piece, this vehicle offers the raw, analog feedback sought by purists in an unblemished, showroom-quality presentation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
