    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a showroom-quality masterpiece that has been preserved with obsessive care. This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that remains entirely free of chips, swirls, or imperfections. Every body panel is laser-straight, reflecting its life spent exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Step inside to an interior that looks and smells brand new; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard remains factory-fresh with every electronic component functioning flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history from day one. It drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new vehicle. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
