      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis integrity is superlative, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement and a meticulously maintained high-pressure VANOS system. The exterior retains its factory depth with no clear coat degradation, while the underside remains free of corrosion. Performance is sharpened by a variable M differential lock and a suspension setup that retains its original damping profile and bushing elasticity. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key example for the serious collector.",
